a = 'http://example.org/mdc'
b = 'http://example.org/smoo'
self._init_conf({DEFAULT_CONTEXT_KEY: a})
with patch('importlib.import_module') as im:

    def f(ctx):
        ctx.new_context(b)

        'test')), {URIRef(a), URIRef(b)})
